metadata.name: calm sunset in a dystopian future
metadata.description:
Genesis Open Edition minted on Manifold.

It just takes one incident for you to connect back to nature. 

This week was wild for me. From my NFTs being hacked to the hacker stealing and deleting my social media accounts that I built for 10 years. This open edition is start of a new journey from me in NFTs again as the hacker couldn't take away my art or mind. I still didn't lose hope and will come back stronger than ever xx. 

Thanks to my friends and followers in NFT Space for supporting me and showing my art journey the love. 

New instagram: https://www.instagram.com/0xnafay/
